#: ../../../reference/random/index.rst:15
msgid ""
"The :mod:`numpy.random` module implements pseudo-random number generators "
"(PRNGs or RNGs, for short) with the ability to draw samples from a variety "
"of probability distributions. In general, users will create a `Generator` "
"instance with `default_rng` and call the various methods on it to obtain "
"samples from different distributions."
msgstr ""

